actionConfiguration.body:
INSERT INTO ot_integration_user_details (
    `ARN_NO`,
    `User_ID`,
    `Employee_ID`,
    `Name_of_user`,
    `Email_ID`,
    `Mobile_Number`,
    `Created_by`,
    `Created_date`,
    `modified_by`,
    `modified_date`,
    `authorised_by`,
    `authorised_date`,
    `act_Created_date`,
    `act_modified_date`,
    `act_authorised_date`,
    `data_process_state`,
    `error_reason`
    ) VALUES (
    {{this.params.arnNo}},
    {{this.params.userId}},
    null,
    {{this.params.userName}},
    {{this.params.email}},
    {{this.params.mobile}},
    {{this.params.createdBy}},
    {{this.params.createdDate}},
    {{this.params.modifiedBy}},
    {{this.params.modifiedDate}},
    null,
    null,
    null,
    null,
    null,
    null,
    null
);
